Class NullStorageManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.storage.StorageManager
      • com.yahoo.bullet.storage.NullStorageManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AutoCloseable

    public class NullStorageManager
extends StorageManager
    A default implementation that does nothing if you do not want to use a StorageManager.
